## 4. Database Initialization

### 4.1 Automatic Migrations

The API service automatically executes database migrations on startup. Migration logic is embedded in the binary via the `sqlx::migrate!()` macro at compile time and executed via `MIGRATOR.run(&pool).await` at runtime.

Key information in startup logs:

```
INFO api: Running embedded database migrations...
INFO api: Database migrations complete
```

### 4.2 Migration File Location

