### 4.3 Reset Database

If you need to completely reset the database (**WARNING: deletes all data**):

```bash
docker compose down -v    # Delete data volumes
docker compose up -d postgres redis   # Restart
# Then restart API service, migrations will run automatically
```

### 4.4 Manual Seed Data Execution

```bash
# Method 1: Use psql client (requires local psql installation)
export DATABASE_URL="postgresql://postgres:postgres@127.0.0.1:5432/online_judge"
bash scripts/bootstrap_demo.sh

# Method 2: Through psql in Docker container
bash scripts/bootstrap_demo.sh
# Script automatically detects: uses local psql if available, otherwise uses docker compose exec
```

